                    <span>If you are into DB theory, and you want to gain a strong understanding of it, this is one of the best avenues to get you there.  There's not one single thing about this book that isn't totally great.  Everything, everything about it is first rate.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Amazing for Engineering Students</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
